@startuml
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title System Sequence Diagram (SSD) - US003: Register New Employee

autonumber

actor "System Administrator" as Admin
participant ":System" as System

activate Admin

    Admin -> System : requests to register a new employee
    activate System

    System --> Admin : list the available roles
    deactivate System

    Admin -> System : provide the roles of the new employee
    activate System



    System --> Admin : list the available agencies
    deactivate System

    Admin -> System : select the agency from the list
        activate System



    System --> Admin : requests the name, email, the passport card number,   \ntax number, contact telephone number and address
    deactivate System

    Admin -> System : provide the necessary data
        activate System




    System --> Admin : shows the data and requests a confirmation
    deactivate System

    Admin -> System : confirm the information
    activate System

    System --> Admin : validate the data and display operation success message
    System --> Admin : send the password to the employee's email

    deactivate System

@enduml
